{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"569ad2d37c","title":"对美国《锤与钢新闻通讯》一篇文章的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6bd7fc7ff9","index":0,"year":1964,"month":5,"day":28,"articleId":"569ad2d37c"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/46-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji46":{"comments":[{"id":"4aab2f29c9","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"569ad2d37c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在1964年5月27日《参考消息》登载的文章摘要《号召击败美国对南越的侵略，并揭露赫鲁晓夫和美共领导的两面手法》旁边。这篇摘要摘自美国《锤与钢新闻通讯》1964年4月份发表的一篇文章。文章说，赫鲁晓夫频徒集团言不由夷地要求美国军队撤出南越，但他们同时又称赞约翰逊总统是爱好和平和合乎情理的。这种两面派的政策是说明修正主义投降行径的又一个例子。美国共产党领导附和赫鲁晓夫的路线。他们一方面假装同情受到侵略的人，一方面又称赞约翰逊政府。"},{"id":"ca4bd68521","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"569ad2d37c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈伯达，当时任中共中央政治局候补委员、中央政治研究室主任、毛泽东的秘书。"}],"contents":[{"id":"91296daabd","type":"title","text":"对美国《锤与钢新闻通讯》一篇文章的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"569ad2d37c"},{"id":"4aab2f29c9","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达同志阅。这是一篇好文章，用简单的语言，说清楚了一个大问题。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"569ad2d37c"},{"id":"ca4bd68521","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"569ad2d37c"},{"id":"f0e5e5e71a","type":"paragraph","text":"五月廿八日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"569ad2d37c"}],"page":{"id":"dd98c15ef0","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"569ad2d37c","start":373,"end":373}}}},"__N_SSG":true}